name: Strawberry Dream
description: Strawberry Dream is a hybrid cross of the Blue Dream and Strawberry Cough strains. With a potency similar to Blue Dream and a smell of sweet strawberries, this sativa-dominant strain will bring considerable head effects.
attributes_title: Uplifted, Creative, Energetic, Relaxed, Euphoric, Stress, Depression, Lack of Appetite, Pain, Insomnia, Dry Mouth, Dry Eyes, Dizzy, Paranoid, Anxious
